content:
Last month, Blur delayed the unlocking of its token, <a href="https://twitter.com/blur_io/status/1616125798951571456?s=20&amp;t=vCUoRYK7mzg3H6YoGzgN9A" data-v-f87c67ca="">saying&nbsp;that</a> an "extra two weeks will allow us to deliver a launch that hasn’t been done before." Blur orchestrated three airdrops last year, delivering "care packages" to traders which contained an undisclosed number of blur tokens.&nbsp;<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
Tuesday was the first opportunity for NFT traders to not only know how many tokens they had been awarded but also to start trading them on the open market.&nbsp;
